msgid ""
"**YunoHost** is a system that installs itself on a **server**  \n"
"and allows you to install and maintain - **with very little technical "
"knowledge** -  \n"
"digital services (apps) **that you control**."
msgstr ""
"**YunoHost** es un sistèma que s'installa sus un **servidor**\n"
"e vos permet d'installar e manténer - **amb plan paucas coneissenças "
"tecnicas** -\n"
"de servicis numerics (aplicacions) **que contrarotlatz**."

