msgid "Donate to YunoHost!"
msgstr "Donatz a YunoHost&nbsp;!"

msgid ""
"YunoHost has been around **since 2012** and is essentially developed **on a "
"voluntary basis** and **outside the commercial sector**."
msgstr ""
"YunoHost existís **dempuèi 2012** e es desvolopat essencialament **de faiçon "
"benevòla** e **en defòra del sector comercial**."

msgid ""
"YunoHost is a modest project in terms of the resources it mobilizes - yet an "
"ambitious one, as much for its activism as for its technical and interface "
"design, as well as for the required perseverance to package and maintain the "
"hundreds of applications in our catalog."
msgstr ""
"YunoHost es un projècte modèst al respècte de las ressorsas que mobiliza - "
"mas ambiciós, tant per son activisme coma per sa concepcion tecnica e "
"d'interfàcia, e tanben per la perseverança necessària per empaquetar e "
"manténer las centenas d'aplicacions de nòstre catalòg."

msgid ""
"If, like us, you'd like to see the project **continue to function**, evolve "
"to **meet its promises**, and allow us to **take care of the community**, "
"this is where you can donate!"
msgstr ""
"Se, coma nosautres, desiratz que lo projècte **contunhe de foncionar**, "
"qu'evolucione per **téner sas promessas** e que nos permeta de **prendre "
"suènh de la comunautat**, es aicí que podètz far un don !"

