msgid "Roadmap and dreammap"
msgstr "Fuèlh de rota e fuèlh de sòmi"

msgid ""
"We're publishing a roadmap here to give a clearer idea of what we plan to "
"develop. It does **NOT** constitutes a promise because it is *dependent on "
"the availability and energies of volunteers*. It is therefore subject to "
"change at any time."
msgstr ""
"Publicam un fuèlh de rota per vos donar una idèa melhora de çò que prevesèm "
"de desvolopar. Aquò constituís **PAS** un engatjament, pr'amor que depend de "
"la disponibilitat e de l'energia dels benevòls. Es doncas susceptible "
"d'èsser modificat a tot moment."

msgid "Timescale depend on grant / donations"
msgstr ""

msgid "Checkout the dedicated roadmap page"
msgstr "Veire la pagina dedicada al fuèlh de rota"

msgid "General questions about donations"
msgstr "Questions generalas a prepaus dels dons"

msgid "Will my donation be tax deductible?"
msgstr "Mon don serà deductible dels impòsts?"

msgid ""
"At this time, we do not provide tax-deductible donation receipts. We can, "
"however, issue donation receipts for your accounting purposes."
msgstr ""
"Pel moment, fornissèm pas de recebuts de don per deduccion fiscala. Pasmens, "
"podèm emetre de recebuts de don per vòstra comptabilitat."

msgid ""
"My donation is not sent to YunoHost but to the Support Self-Hosting "
"association. Is this normal?"
msgstr ""
"Mon don es pas mandat a YunoHost mas a l'associacion Support Self-Hosting. "
"Es normal ?"

msgid ""
"Yes, that's expected, Support Self-Hosting is the association that enables "
"the YunoHost project to collect donations and pay expenses."
msgstr ""
"Òc, aquò's normal, Support Self-Hosting es l'associacion que permet al "
"projècte YunoHost de collectar de dons e de pagar las despensas."

msgid "Can I become a member of the Support Self-Hosting association?"
msgstr "Pòdi venir membre de l'associacion Support Self-Hosting ?"

msgid ""
"No: this is an association whose members are chosen by co-option.<br>We "
"don't think you need to be a member of Support Self-Hosting to contribute to "
"the YunoHost project. Anyone can come and help on most of our projects, and "
"we do our best to welcome volunteers."
msgstr ""
"Non: es una associacion que sos membres son causits per cooptacion."
"<br>Pensam pas qu'avètz besonh d'èsser membre de Support Self-Hosting per "
"contribuir al projècte YunoHost. Cadun pòt venir ajudar sus la màger part de "
"nòstres projèctes, e fasèm de nòstre melhor per aculhir los benevòls."

msgid ""
"I can't make a recurring donation, but I'd like to support YunoHost. What "
"can I do?"
msgstr ""
"Pòdi pas far un don recurrent, mas m’agradariá de sosténer YunoHost. De qué "
"pòdi far ?"

msgid ""
"Thank you for your support and commitment.<br>You can make a one-off "
"donation directly from the [donate.yunohost.org](https://donate.yunohost."
"org) page."
msgstr ""
"Mercés per vòstre sosten e vòstre engatjament.<br>Podètz far un don pontual "
"directament dempuèi la pagina [donate.yunohost.org](https://donate.yunohost."
"org)."

msgid ""
"I've made a monthly donation but I've made a mistake in the amount or I'd "
"like to change it. How do I proceed?"
msgstr ""
"Ai fach un don mensual mas me soi enganat/enganada dins la soma o la "
"voldriái cambiar. Cossí devi far ?"

msgid ""
"We cannot change the amount for future debits.<br>But you can cancel your "
"previous donation and start a new one by using the “Manage your monthly "
"donation” link on our [donate.yunohost.org](https://donate.yunohost.org) "
"page."
msgstr ""
"Podèm pas cambiar lo montant dels prelevaments futurs.<br>Mas podètz anullar "
"vòstre don precedent e ne començar un novèl en utilizant lo ligam « Gerir "
"vòstre don mensual » sus nòstra pagina [donate.yunohost.org](https://donate."
"yunohost.org)."

msgid ""
"I am currently making a recurring donation but my credit card has expired. "
"What should I do?"
msgstr ""
"Fau actualament un don recurrent mas ma carta de crèdit a expirat. Qué devi "
"far ?"

msgid ""
"Typically, your recurring donation is automatically interrupted once your "
"card has been deactivated.<br>To update your bank details with Support Self-"
"Hosting, please complete the form on the [donate.yunohost.org](https://"
"donate.yunohost.org) page as if it were your first donation."
msgstr ""
"Normalament, vòstre don recurrent s'arrèsta automaticament un còp que vòstra "
"carta es desactivada.<br>Per metre a jorn vòstras coordenadas bancàrias amb "
"Support Self-Hosting,, vos cal emplenar lo formulari sus la pagina [donate."
"yunohost.org](https://donate.yunohost.org) coma s'èra vòstre primièr don."

msgid ""
"My organization doesn't have a credit card, but would like to make a "
"donation. How do I go about it?"
msgstr ""
"Mon organizacion a pas de carta de crèdit, mas voldriá far un don. Cossí o "
"pòdi far ?"

msgid ""
"You can contact us so that we can provide you with an IBAN to make a bank "
"transfer."
msgstr ""
"Nos podètz contactar per que vos balhem un IBAN per far un virament bancari."

msgid "I'd like to stop a recurring donation. What can I do?"
msgstr "Voldriái arrestar un don recurrent. Qué pòdi far ?"

msgid ""
"You can cancel your donation by using the “Manage your monthly donation” "
"link on our [donate.yunohost.org](https://donate.yunohost.org) page."
msgstr ""
"Podètz anullar vòstre don en utilizant lo ligam « Gerir vòstre don mensual » "
"sus nòstra pagina [donate.yunohost.org](https://donate.yunohost.org)."

msgid ""
"With **YunoHost**, easily manage %(a server|a cloud|a website|mailboxes|a "
"wiki|a social network|a video library|a blog|surveys|an accounting board|a "
"game server|a forum|a chat|an ERP)%  \n"
"for your friends, your association, your company"
msgstr ""
"Amb **YunoHost**, gerissètz facilament %(un servidor|un nívol|un site web|de "
"bóstias de recepcion|un wiki|un malhum social|una videotèca|un blòg|de "
"sondatges|un tabulador de comptabilitat|un servidor de jòc|un forum|un chat|"
"un ERP)%   \n"
"per vòstres amics, vòstra associacion, vòstra entrepresa"

