msgid ""
"**YunoHost** is a non-profit **technocritical** project, developed and "
"maintained by **volunteers**."
msgstr ""
"**YunoHost** es un projècte **tecnocritic sens tòca lucrativa**, desvolopat "
"e mantengut per de **benevòls**."

msgid ""
"We advocate a **decentralized** Internet, with **open**, **interoperable** "
"technologies that **respect privacy** and **empowers people**."
msgstr ""
"Defendèm un **internet descentralizat**, de tecnologias **dobèrtas**, "
"**interoperablas**, que **respèctan la vida privada** e que dònan de "
"l'**autonomia** e de **poder al mai grand nombre**."

msgid ""
"In addition, we aim to **give materiality back to the digital**, and "
"encourage **sobriety** and **reuse**."
msgstr ""
"En mai, desiram **redonar de materialitat al numeric**, encoratjar la "
"**sobrietat** e lo **reemplec**."

msgid "Code repositories"
msgstr "Depaus de còdi"

msgid "They support us <3"
msgstr "Nos sostenon <3"

msgid ""
"We are thankful for our sponsors providing us with infrastructure and grants!"
msgstr ""
"Sèm reconeissents envers nòstres mecènas que nos sostenon financièrament o "
"via de dons d'infraestructura !"

